## Installation

### Download from the App Store (iPhone and iPad)

1. Open the App Store on your iPhone or iPad.
2. Search for "Word to Audio Converter" in the search bar.
3. Tap on the app icon in the search results.
4. On the app page, tap the "Get" or "Download" button.
5. Authenticate with your Apple ID, if prompted.
6. Wait for the app to download and install on your device.
7. Once installed, the app icon will appear on your home screen.

## Features

Word to Audio Converter offers a range of features to enhance your Language Translation and Learning experience. Explore the following capabilities:

### Offline Translation

Word to Audio Converter works with completely AI Trained Language Models. Totally we support 33 Languages in offline. 
With our Advanced AI powered Word to Audio Converter, you can convert any type of Word Document into Audiobooks with 33 different languages without depending on the internet. 
Our models are fast and accurate.

### Word Viewer

Now you can view Word Document from our Word to Audio Converter itself before wants to convert it. 

### Word Audio

All you need to Pick the Word from the files that you want to convert into Audio using the browse option, select your source and target language that you want your Word Audio file to be converted, set speech rate depends on your choice. It is fast and accurate.

